{"tid":1799232,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找有野心有能力嘅巴絲","createTime":"2019-12-26T20:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T04:59:26.000Z","uid":208579,"like":23,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"d1fc0a00ee4101ecc985055e19c8a54474c1439e","tid":1799232,"uid":208579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T20:11:49.000Z","msg":"雖然家庭環境資源唔算好豐富，但由細到大一直都好有野心想做大事，想開公司，亦想一手一腳創造一個帝國。不過我知道宜家嘅我仲未夠經驗、能力同資本做到。所以想組一個小群組，大家互相學習，發揮所長，到到時機成熟，大家一齊去創一番事業。時間唔喺講緊未來一年二年，而喺五年十年咁計。<br />\n<br />\n呢個小群體嘅目標喺令大家成長，同大家要努力學唔同嘅嘢，可以喺經濟、藝術、環境、政治、天文地理、科技、醫學。我希望一直都Keep到落去，到最後可以成為大家一生嘅同伴。我明白喺網上搵可能好奇怪，但我知道網上有好多人喺我一世都未必會遇到，所以用呢個方法搵你地。<br />\n<br />\n小小嘅自我介紹，我宜家喺讀緊大學，主修BBA會計學。基本上我對所有嘢都有好強嘅好奇心，最近比較中意嘅喺研究科技轉變嘅商機。之前有研究過歷史、Python、日文、韓文、樓市、言語、遊戲研發、煮嘢食、坑渠結構、風對樓宇影響等等。<br />\n<br />\n如果你地有想一齊改變世界嘅野心同決心，來吧！"},{"pid":"59ce13b7de077bd77bbde120e0ac654c0df80760","tid":1799232,"uid":181767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T22:08:19.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e1edac46418ff2b5471ead3eb4b756c2b3728bf2","tid":1799232,"uid":98680,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T22:11:26.000Z","msg":"睇完你編野，感覺似倫敦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92512a644f373389cf51756a96d5c1fbe154a33","tid":1799232,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T22:20:03.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"29cf764118eae50c7aee55a00d78ea9785e27265","tid":1799232,"uid":208579,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"e1edac46418ff2b5471ead3eb4b756c2b3728bf2","tid":1799232,"uid":98680,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T22:11:26.000Z","msg":"睇完你編野，感覺似倫敦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"俾你講完，我都覺得似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我可以解釋點解唔喺倫敦金。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦金其實都搵唔到好多錢，只喺食中間嘅中介費。再加埋佢犯法，基本上run唔到好耐，充其量可以話喺短期營銷。但呢個如果喺企業成立嘅開始，不單喺企業形象唔好，連自己個人名譽都有問題，例子喺t-series ，類似佢地俾pew一直追擊以盜版起手一樣（雖然佢地算成功咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），但同我嘅諗法有啲出入。<br />\n<br />\n利申：純粹個人意見，期待有另一個觀點大家切磋交流。"},{"pid":"a1dbaecd8e8b523ae3e40959095cdeed01fd78ff","tid":1799232,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"咁你專咩"},{"pid":"42d0b6a5f250fa6786763b2530a5ad171538787c","tid":1799232,"uid":228143,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:23:42.000Z","msg":"屌即係交換技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講咁多4個字總結"},{"pid":"0f1cf016802ac384577c2bde70277a207978df78","tid":1799232,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得係好事  有付出有回報  好多tg都做緊啦"},{"pid":"3b1205c6e91fa67a9665bee30337ff5266d2f49a","tid":1799232,"uid":68430,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"我急不及待好好的玩了"},{"pid":"b5aa956cc7c5dea80c7aafac397b4693f2d3e507","tid":1799232,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"我都讀緊bba <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n張華峰 ！ 爆血管！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2fbc4f550f8d3f376db561af9f55478755e91362","tid":1799232,"uid":208579,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42d0b6a5f250fa6786763b2530a5ad171538787c","tid":1799232,"uid":228143,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:23:42.000Z","msg":"屌即係交換技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講咁多4個字總結"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"都似嘅，不過喺想大家一齊做好一樣嘢，一個人嘅能力有限，你max到能力值當然好勁，但要成為最強、突圍而出，我覺得有唔同性格、優點嘅同伴可以將成就推得更高更遠。（有啲似海賊王添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"d51e2128dd91f843afdcf9fbc388a5b5622f3667","tid":1799232,"uid":208579,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a1dbaecd8e8b523ae3e40959095cdeed01fd78ff","tid":1799232,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"咁你專咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:33:22.000Z","msg":"比較強嘅地方有商業頭腦同智識、自學過編程、音樂都略懂、將程序系統化同簡化、心理學（少少）。"},{"pid":"a8ef3195bb6f23b35b940e6eec0a85f8ff5d5c3a","tid":1799232,"uid":31386,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"有啲中二病 但支持你追夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc59f1a2951e2bb9a5aedc97dade72505448059","tid":1799232,"uid":122445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T04:10:06.000Z","msg":"精神上支持你"},{"pid":"d74d9e35d0cb4ca76ddddaf08ff77d9e152d8099","tid":1799232,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:46:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"bebe59deb983f18f31c8b57212da66ce3fbc63ea","tid":1799232,"uid":68944,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:06:39.000Z","msg":"一手一腳創造一個帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fe1ec30f1487e69573eb975bd050d431cf73dc","tid":1799232,"uid":308732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:10:57.000Z","msg":"同你同野心<br />\n但我接受唔到同人合作 我對好多野好有主見<br />\n你覺得適唔適合加入你<br />\n<br />\n利申 脾氣好"},{"pid":"c2ed457fbdb725e597c2146dd2b7dd5edcbe70e3","tid":1799232,"uid":208579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57fe1ec30f1487e69573eb975bd050d431c